description: Richard Felix, The Historian from TV's Most Haunted is our guest on the first hour of Darkness Radio!  Richard regales us of tales of how he got into the paranormal, the history of how Most Haunted got started, some of Most Haunted's best cases, and some behind the scenes goodies!
